Title: The Dryad Garden
Description:
$n, there is a situation I am personally concerned about. 

A garden cared for by my kin, the dryads, has suffered from growing pains amidst Amirdrassil's growth.

An overwrought druid currently tends the garden, but I suspect he will need more assistance than he has requested. 

Please assist him in his task on my behalf.
ObjectivesText: Speak with Ethidris Creekward in the Root-Bound Sanctuary.
